    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This page is to summarize the analysis of CDD_isd module"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ISD = Island state detector"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Island state detector is responsible for detecting and moving safety island subsystem (SAILSS) into Island state at different stages of the chip cold boot, SAIL Low Power state and during main domain (MD) and SAIL crash/faults."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Island state detector is responsible for generation of SAIL_PS_HOLD and SAIL_TO_MD_PS_HOLD"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Typical use case"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "The Island state detector is responsible for detecting errors and moving SAILSS into Island state during chip cold boot and crash/fault",
        "Main domain bootup status of each boot stage should be informed to SAIL and to the external MCU",
        "Any known reset requested by main domain should be handled in SAIL ISD. Any known error on SAIL that requires SoC reset or EDL mode entry should be communicated to MD."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Configuration parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Jayaraj Praveen (BCSC/ENG1) To anlayze more on the meaning of these status"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "IsdMDStatusType"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "XBL_SEC_BOOT_SUCCESS",
        "DDR_READY - Pre init Mailbox here",
        "XBL_LOADER_BOOT_SUCCESS",
        "MD_VSENSE_SUCCESS",
        "TZ_SUCCESS",
        "QHEE_SUCCESS",
        "UEFI_SUCCESS",
        "ABL_SUCCESS",
        "S1_READY_SUCCES S - Handshake is success with Mian domain - Init Mailbox here",
        "MB_READY_SUCCESS",
        "ISD_MD2SAIL_STATUS_FAILED"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Isd_StateType"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "UNDEFINED_STATE",
        "ISLAND_STATE",
        "NORMAL_STATE",
        "SOC_WARM_RESET",
        "SOC_SHUTDOWN",
        "SOC_EDL",
        "SOC_HARD_RESET",
        "SOC_CRASH_RESET"
      ]
    },
